                            h2 Love Bombing
                            p Scammers often employ a technique known as love bombing, where they send the first message with a lot of compliments on you.
                            p While Compliments can make you feel good, it's important to be careful about their intentions, especially when you're just getting to know someone.


                    //- Card 2 
                    .ui.basic.card
                        .content
                            h2 Establishing Trust and Authenticity
                            p To impress you, scammers will disclose details about their personality or their successful careers in order to gain trust and build credibility. They portray themselves as good, morally upright persons by using words and phrases with religious connotations. For example, use of adjectives such as "honest" and "sincere".

